title: Limit Cake Voting power to 100
body: To facilitate a more equal and equitable decision making process that encompasses all community members, I propose that voting power is limited up to 100 cake per person. This still gives a range of voting power, while giving weight to the decisions of all investors and not allowing disproportional governance to those with heavy financial interest.
author: 0x8bD115b9D8078718c4dfAc29d8eDAFb15D7647b7
